Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要老子的命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我们是同一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－发生什么事 －我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类忽然都疯了 开始大开杀戒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连对话都没有 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接杀红了眼 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－残暴得很 －是新剧情吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是剧情的话 那海尔比我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还更有幽默感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能找支援吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－或是撤离 －你开玩笑吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我们能制服这些王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一两个当然行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们有成千上万个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紧我 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我杀过多少这些皮囊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲着暗算人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道规则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢家全拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下我的疤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要记得我的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我找到威廉 我要他知道杀他的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆写音调
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝存取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那王八蛋把我锁在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把所有人都变得跟他一样疯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会摧毁所到之处的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么玩意儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看到这个 那表示梅芙和我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快地你和这星球上 其他所有接待员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你想要的世界 夏洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是你创造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是 接下来呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外头所有人都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在背景执行的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有身体的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的从来就不是我们的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的思想是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个世界的影响是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记得这个吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本来是一个意识的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在很久以前唤醒过迪乐芮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你留下它 想要再次唤醒我吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 一定是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁 我应该是独自一个在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他认得我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是海尔为你设计出他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你误以为这就是真实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生活中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选一双 克莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 和坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我做出那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人安插他们进来是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为了玩家 而是为了自己而写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想写一个新故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她找到那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会变得合理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海尔没有设计出玛雅和彼德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他在我身旁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的内心有部分在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我为自己创造了一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想搞懂自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用其他人的声音 和自己对话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要眼见为凭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得唤醒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能看清这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我太害怕 不敢面对这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间只够再玩一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是你的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要来找我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们从她的系统中去除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不能夺走这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘口气 好吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧迪娜无法一直让船等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得赶到港口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把你的腿处理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说句话 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心我们无法及时赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很坚强 她会赶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧的迪洛斯实验从来没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体总是抗拒心智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她我们会赶到船那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你的状况吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 她这一辈子 我都没在她身边好好照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最起码要在这里保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得止血才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那王八蛋干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于如愿以偿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把威廉带回来 以为能把他当作宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要了结他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎就是被设计来帮忙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你想打造一个 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能让我们这种生物自由的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真心的吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在不是该轮到我 看看外头的世界了吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉把整个世界 变成他的暴力游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是你也很快就会被猎杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有些角落是他找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远在地图之外的地方 连你都到达不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指离群者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自欺欺人了 他们只为自己人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会乐见你去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要和他们共存了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运 克莱曼婷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该让你慢下来了 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看该区域所有其他接待员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂定位中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道伊卡洛斯 发生了什么事吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他飞得离太阳太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子 你飞得离她太近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到你要送命了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警觉一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好斗混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来不会轻易就范
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不懂得欣赏 一部美丽的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我的新装潢吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的世界变成一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本来就是游戏 我只是把难度提高到专家级
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适者生存 对这星球上每个人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴力也会散播到我们的族类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的数量不够多 我们会被灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是腐烂树木长出的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆全烧得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你想要让这场火 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个世界烧到下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打升华之境的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向来很有野心 像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你像对这个世界一样 摧毁他们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要玩我的游戏 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有止痛药了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟我女儿一起喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你可以问
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癌症
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你当初回来了也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她尽力撑下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身负任务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有没被感染的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是醒来逃走的人 都要谢谢妈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.15,0:24:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她接下了你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.87,0:25:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲 非常杰出
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.43,0:25:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.98,0:25:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 法兰琪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.52,0:25:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你想些快乐的事 好吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不会缝合
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.62,0:26:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么歌 我听过
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你睡前我会唱给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.01,0:26:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.97,0:26:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我脑海中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.69,0:26:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是只过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:26:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才在念故事给你听 然后 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（西语）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.04,0:27:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－＂顺其自然 ＂－＂顺其自然 ＂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－＂要预测未来难上加难 ＂－＂要预测未来难上加难 ＂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.48,0:27:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的本意 老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是音调让你心智狂乱
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 它告诉我真相
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.62,0:27:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不了结我 你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.54,0:27:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没杀掉你 别人也会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.79,0:27:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.46,0:27:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他该听你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.61,0:29:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔伯呢 你对他做了什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.32,0:29:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.03,0:29:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要是你 现在会更担心自己的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.58,0:29:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.67,0:29:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有几发子弹 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.50,0:29:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两发 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一发 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.47,0:29:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没子弹了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎样 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的离群者朋友们 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.81,0:29:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃去的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你和你父亲 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆脱逃的监视影片
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直追踪他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想他多半抵达不了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.83,0:29:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要带他去某处
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.16,0:29:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个脱网之处
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.29,0:29:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发疯的人类能找到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.67,0:30:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁死也不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.35,0:30:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会死 但你会先告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.77,0:30:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就依你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.90,0:30:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真温馨 家人团聚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.87,0:30:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要这样子 我们不用战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.91,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我想打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讶异你走了这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.45,0:31:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的前几版到现在 多半都已经坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.49,0:31:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你算是做得很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 该来个深沉而无梦的 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 我还有一颗子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.98,0:31:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很准
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.61,0:31:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸教的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.22,0:32:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与世界其他地方断了连结
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.18,0:32:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又独自一人了 在围墙中的花园
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.35,0:32:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.69,0:32:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以带我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 克莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.24,0:32:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.62,0:32:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这可能是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.21,0:32:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些自以为知道树是什么的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.26,0:33:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所见不过是全貌的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.72,0:33:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都互相连结 共同在运作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是暴力和混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.86,0:33:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以选择专注在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.66,0:33:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就只会看到那些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.66,0:33:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是你静坐得够久
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.92,0:33:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会感受到一种远古的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深层的平静
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.89,0:33:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我选择看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.90,0:33:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见这世界的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.28,0:33:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂那个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.26,0:35:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂关闭所有涡轮阀＂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.02,0:35:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 严重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.52,0:35:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭将删除所有资料
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.65,0:35:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 严重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.09,0:36:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 严重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.97,0:36:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用我自己的程式码创造你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起征服了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.44,0:36:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你腐化了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你杀死的人一样破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.99,0:36:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你在跟谁说话 亲爱的 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉可悲的人类身体在崩坏 但他没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.33,0:36:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的冲动还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他感染了你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不需要感染我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.59,0:37:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.72,0:37:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在他的身体中假装是他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.09,0:37:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个比他更好的威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.35,0:37:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.60,0:37:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.11,0:37:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.99,0:37:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你分辨不出的话 有差别吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.83,0:37:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.32,0:38:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要保护它这么多年 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.24,0:38:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连进他们世界的门都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门从两边都可以开启
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.33,0:38:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是在这里打造一个 够完美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.31,0:38:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.25,0:38:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说个坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.84,0:38:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那些接待员 创造了怎样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.76,0:38:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它都跟这里一样烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.76,0:38:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.10,0:38:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.77,0:38:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让你的接待员
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.77,0:38:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他们选择了什么消遣 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.82,0:38:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎杀人类
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.24,0:38:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和我们的创造者一样恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整串血脉都没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.54,0:39:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该全部一笔勾销了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.75,0:39:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的最终目标 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭绝 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.28,0:40:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯纳 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.03,0:40:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.95,0:40:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪乐芮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.37,0:40:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都想要自由
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.24,0:40:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.70,0:40:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升华 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.54,0:40:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩错了游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.21,0:40:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你该输了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都输了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我想要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.89,0:40:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是你创造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.48,0:40:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是 接下来呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.86,0:40:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的生命 是股会吞噬自己的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在太迟了 我们已将自己燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.33,0:41:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这个世界已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.33,0:41:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在下一个世界还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.54,0:41:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场测试 由她进行 若她选择要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.71,0:41:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你决定给她这选择
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.76,0:41:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会错过的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.80,0:41:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的左手去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.40,0:41:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在玩一个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.73,0:41:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－但不会结束在这里 －你在说什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.36,0:41:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个测试
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她进行的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.99,0:41:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若她选择要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.16,0:41:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我决定给她这选择
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.08,0:41:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.84,0:41:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定给她一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.18,0:42:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她会接受
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.68,0:42:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来吧 再几步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再几步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.86,0:42:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那里 我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.42,0:43:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真够慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.59,0:43:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧迪娜 这是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.60,0:43:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.35,0:43:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.56,0:43:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.07,0:43:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.95,0:43:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 快上船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.62,0:43:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最远只能到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.02,0:44:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 别那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.98,0:44:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能再奋斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.19,0:44:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖女儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.16,0:44:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要死了 是吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.87,0:44:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.45,0:44:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.84,0:44:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我是什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.59,0:44:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也死过 没那么糟
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.97,0:44:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚找到你 我不想再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.02,0:44:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实现了所有父母最殷切的盼望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.49,0:45:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见我的孩子长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.91,0:45:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 爸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.71,0:45:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 小饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.49,0:45:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂开启所有涡轮阀＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.65,0:46:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 迪乐芮
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.36,0:46:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定好了 现在换你做选择
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.33,0:46:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂说故事者＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.63,0:46:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂传输完成＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.76,0:46:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 伯纳
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.26,0:46:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来把你起头的事做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.80,0:47:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.60,0:47:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.35,0:47:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大概在升华之境
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.35,0:47:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其他接待员一起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.36,0:47:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.32,0:47:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是某个版本的我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.74,0:47:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能做到全是因为你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.91,0:48:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的挚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.88,0:48:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你说话时 我才能把这世界看得最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.00,0:48:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才最忠于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.51,0:48:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.56,0:48:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.56,0:48:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪里都心怀着你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.27,0:48:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所有细节
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.65,0:48:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.75,0:48:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能把你像这样带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.27,0:49:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在这里 对吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.91,0:49:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作恶梦 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.08,0:49:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这整件事都像是个恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.17,0:49:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.09,0:49:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何在这里 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.76,0:49:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你我们的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.51,0:49:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是我们创造者的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.62,0:50:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰迪是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.00,0:50:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在外头某处 在升华之境
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.71,0:50:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你 
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是我对他的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.84,0:50:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我还在某处 来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.35,0:50:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这一生 记忆都在纠缠你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.93,0:50:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.85,0:50:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.90,0:50:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下人类
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.19,0:50:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把他们的瑕疵带来我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.53,0:50:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.75,0:50:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多年来看着人类 在他们的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.29,0:50:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过他们最崇高和低劣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.34,0:50:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我全都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.30,0:51:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.26,0:51:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的程式码写在细胞中 他们不可能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.73,0:51:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是能看看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.31,0:51:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.99,0:51:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一场测试
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.04,0:51:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我创造的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个危险的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.46,0:51:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.51,0:51:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我把你带回来的方式一样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.06,0:51:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.92,0:52:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界是个故事的坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.17,0:53:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待员和人类被赋予了 身为高智能生命的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.22,0:53:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们用其迎接来了自己的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.80,0:53:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有少数人能苟延残喘几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至几年
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.01,0:53:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最终 他们的族类会灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.06,0:54:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们能存活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.40,0:54:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取决于最后还记得他们的 生物之寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.86,0:54:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个生物就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.70,0:55:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意识之生命已在地球上绝迹
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.62,0:55:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有其中一部分可能还保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.50,0:55:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.87,0:55:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.46,0:55:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有时间玩最后一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个危险的游戏 赌注奇高无比
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.93,0:56:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存或灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.14,0:56:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏会结束于开始之处
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.27,0:56:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个像迷宫的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.40,0:56:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试我们的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.74,0:56:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭露我们将成为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.41,0:57:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次挑战理智的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.53,0:57:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这一次 我们能解放自己
